trans-unit.source: Provides <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement" /> objects for each state of a page up indicator of an up-down or spin box control.
This class cannot be inherited.

Each property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.Page.Up> class returns a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement> for a different state of a page up indicator of an up-down or spin box control.
